I"ô<p>At the Goodwill store on Haight Street, they display all the donated sweaters in a beautful color spectrum. I photographed them in 2009 with the thought of assembling the images into a larger piece.</p>

<p>In 2022, I created a 4 panel synchronized video display powered by 5 Raspberry Pi computers.</p>

